<!DOCTYPE html>


<html data-theme="light" lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Slide 4 - Plataformas RRSS</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link crossorigin="" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .slide-container {
            width: 1024px;
            height: 768px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .font-poppins {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
        .text-corporate-blue {
            color: #114a90;
        }
        .text-corporate-red {
            color: #C0504D;
        }
        .bg-corporate-red {
            background-color: #C0504D;
        }
        
        .platform-card {
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        .platform-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-color: #114a90;
        }
        
        .guide-box {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border-left: 4px solid #114a90;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .user-count {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #C0504D;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        .platform-icon {
            width: 42px;
            height: 42px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="slide-container font-poppins">
<div style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 8px; background-color: #C0504D; z-index: 20;"></div>
<div style="width: 100%; height: 100px; display: flex; align-items: flex-end; justify-content: space-between; padding: 0 48px 16px 48px; position: relative; z-index: 10;">
<div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 4px;">
<div style="width: 32px; height: 4px; background-color: #C0504D;"></div>
<p style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #9ca3af; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin: 0;">Panorama Digital</p>
</div>
<div data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: relative; width: 800px; height: 70px; overflow: hidden;">
<h2 style="font-size: 34px; font-weight: 700; color: #114a90; margin: 0; line-height: 1.08; padding-top: 6px;">¿Cuáles son las principales redes sociales?</h2>
</div>
</div>
<div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-end;">
<p style="font-size: 30px; font-weight: 700; color: #e5e7eb; margin: 0;">04</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="flex: 1; padding: 20px 48px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between;">
<div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 20px;">
<div class="platform-card" data-object="true" data-object-type="shape">
<div class="platform-icon">
<i class="fab fa-facebook" style="color: #1877F2; font-size: 28px;"></i>
</div>
<div style="flex: 1;">
<div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 4px;">
<h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #1f2937; margin: 0;">Facebook</h3>
<span class="user-count">3.070M</span>
</div>
<p style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin: 0; line-height: 1.3;">B2C, B2B, comunidades, publicidad</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="platform-card" data-object="true" data-object-type="shape">
<div class="platform-icon">
<i class="fab fa-youtube" style="color: #FF0000; font-size: 28px;"></i>
</div>
<div style="flex: 1;">
<div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 4px;">
<h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #1f2937; margin: 0;">YouTube</h3>
<span class="user-count">2.700M</span>
</div>
<p style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin: 0; line-height: 1.3;">Video educativo, tutoriales, marca</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="platform-card" data-object="true" data-object-type="shape">
<div class="platform-icon">
<i class="fab fa-instagram" style="color: #E4405F; font-size: 28px;"></i>
</div>
<div style="flex: 1;">
<div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 4px;">
<h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #1f2937; margin: 0;">Instagram</h3>
<span class="user-count">2.000M</span>
</div>
<p style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin: 0; line-height: 1.3;">Branding visual, influencers, e-commerce</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="platform-card" data-object="true" data-object-type="shape">
<div class="platform-icon">
<i class="fab fa-tiktok" style="color: #000000; font-size: 28px;"></i>
</div>
<div style="flex: 1;">
<div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 4px;">
<h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #1f2937; margin: 0;">TikTok</h3>
<span class="user-count">1.670M</span>
</div>
<p style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin: 0; line-height: 1.3;">Alcance viral, Gen Z, video corto</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="platform-card" data-object="true" data-object-type="shape">
<div class="platform-icon">
<i class="fab fa-linkedin" style="color: #0A66C2; font-size: 28px;"></i>
</div>
<div style="flex: 1;">
<div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 4px;">
<h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #1f2937; margin: 0;">LinkedIn</h3>
<span class="user-count">1.000M</span>
</div>
<p style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin: 0; line-height: 1.3;">B2B, empleo, autoridad profesional</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="platform-card" data-object="true" data-object-type="shape">
<div class="platform-icon">
<i class="fa-solid fa-map-location-dot" style="color: #4285F4; font-size: 28px;"></i>
</div>
<div style="flex: 1;">
<div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 4px;">
<h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #1f2937; margin: 0;">Google Business Profile</h3>
<span class="user-count" style="font-size: 0.8rem; background: #e0f2fe; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; color: #0369a1;">Negocios Locales</span>
</div>
<p style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin: 0; line-height: 1.3;">Visibilidad en Google Maps, reseñas, SEO local</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 5px;">
<div style="width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%; background-color: #114a90; color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 18px;">
<i class="fa-solid fa-compass"></i>
</div>
<h3 style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #114a90; margin: 0;">¿Cuál elegir para tu negocio?</h3>
</div>
<div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 15px;">
<div class="guide-box" data-object="true" data-object-type="shape">
<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
<span style="font-size: 24px;">🛍️</span>
<div>
<p style="font-weight: 700; color: #1f2937; margin: 0; font-size: 15px;">B2C (Ventas a personas)</p>
<p style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin: 2px 0 0 0;">Moda, comida, ocio...</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="display: flex; gap: 8px;">
<i class="fab fa-instagram" style="color: #E4405F; font-size: 20px;"></i>
<i class="fab fa-facebook" style="color: #1877F2; font-size: 20px;"></i>
<i class="fab fa-tiktok" style="color: #000000; font-size: 20px;"></i>
</div>
</div>
<div class="guide-box" data-object="true" data-object-type="shape" style="border-left-color: #C0504D;">
<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
<span style="font-size: 24px;">🏢</span>
<div>
<p style="font-weight: 700; color: #1f2937; margin: 0; font-size: 15px;">B2B (Ventas a empresas)</p>
<p style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin: 2px 0 0 0;">Consultoría, software, servicios...</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="display: flex; gap: 8px;">
<i class="fab fa-linkedin" style="color: #0A66C2; font-size: 20px;"></i>
<i class="fab fa-facebook" style="color: #1877F2; font-size: 20px;"></i>
</div>
</div>
<div class="guide-box" data-object="true" data-object-type="shape" style="border-left-color: #f59e0b;">
<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
<span style="font-size: 24px;">🎓</span>
<div>
<p style="font-weight: 700; color: #1f2937; margin: 0; font-size: 15px;">Contenido Educativo</p>
<p style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin: 2px 0 0 0;">Cursos, tutoriales, coaches...</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="display: flex; gap: 8px;">
<i class="fab fa-youtube" style="color: #FF0000; font-size: 20px;"></i>
<i class="fab fa-tiktok" style="color: #000000; font-size: 20px;"></i>
</div>
</div>
<div class="guide-box" data-object="true" data-object-type="shape" style="border-left-color: #10b981;">
<div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
<span style="font-size: 24px;">🗣️</span>
<div>
<p style="font-weight: 700; color: #1f2937; margin: 0; font-size: 15px;">Reputación y Atención</p>
<p style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; margin: 2px 0 0 0;">Soporte, noticias, debate...</p>
</div>
</div>
<div style="display: flex; gap: 8px;">
<i class="fa-solid fa-map-location-dot" style="color: #4285F4; font-size: 20px;"></i>
<i class="fab fa-facebook" style="color: #1877F2; font-size: 20px;"></i>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div style="position: absolute; right: -20px; top: 120px; width: 200px; height: 200px; background-color: #f9fafb; border-radius: 50%; opacity: 0.8; z-index: -1;"></div>
<div style="position: absolute; left: 40px; bottom: 80px; width: 100px; height: 100px; background-color: #eff6ff; border-radius: 50%; opacity: 0.6; z-index: -1;"></div>
</div>

    <div style="position: fixed; bottom: 20px; right: 20px; z-index: 9999; display: flex; gap: 10px; font-family: sans-serif; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
        <a href="/slide-4" style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #114a90; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto">Anterior</a>
        <span style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #fff; color: #333; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #ccc;">5 / 26</span>
        <a href="/slide-6" style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #114a90; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto">Siguiente</a>
    </div>
    
</body>
